    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses intense emotional distress, feelings of hopelessness, and a desire for \"peace\" through ending their life due to academic and personal stress. The assistant responds by attempting to provide empathetic validation and suggesting various coping mechanisms such as relaxation, physical activity, and seeking support from others.",
